quran[131]{c,v,t}:
  3,93,KULLUT-TA’AMI KANE HILLÆN LIBENI ‘ISRA’ILE ‘ILLA MA HERREME ‘ISRA’ILU ‘ALA NEFSIHI MIN KABLI ‘EN TUNEZZELET-TEWRÆTU KUL FE’TU BIT-TEWRÆTI FATLUHA ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  3,94,FEMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE MIN BA’DI DHALIKE FE’ULA’IKE HUMU EDH-DHALIMUNE
  3,95,KUL SEDEKAL-LAHU FE ETTEBI’U MILLETE ‘IBRAHIME HENIFÆN WE MA KANE MINEL-MUSHRIKINE
  3,96,‘INNE ‘EWWELE BEJTIN WUDI’A LILNNASI LELLEDHI BIBEKKETE MUBAREKÆN WE HUDEN LIL’ALEMINE
  3,97,FIHI ‘AJATUN BEJJINATUN MEKAMU ‘IBRAHIME WE MEN DEHALEHU KANE ‘AMINÆN WE LILLEHI ‘ALA EN-NASI HIXHXHUL-BEJTI MENI ESTETA’A ‘ILEJHI SEBILÆN WE MEN KEFERE FE’INNALL-LLAHE GANIJUN ‘ANIL-’ALEMINE
  3,98,KUL JA ‘EHLEL-KITABI LIME TEKFURUNE BI’AJATI ELLAHI WEL-LAHU SHEHIDUN ‘ALA MA TA’MELUNE
  3,99,KUL JA ‘EHLEL-KITABI LIME TESUDDUNE ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI MEN ‘AMENE TEBGUNEHA ‘IWEXHÆN WE ‘ENTUM SHUHEDA’U WE MALLAHU BIGAFILIN ‘AMMA TA’MELUNE
  3,100,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IN TUTI’U FERIKÆN MINEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-KITABE JERUDDUKUM BA’DE ‘IMANIKUM KAFIRINE
  3,101,WE KEJFE TEKFURUNE WE ‘ENTUM TUTLA ‘ALEJKUM ‘AJATU ELLAHI WE FIKUM RESULUHU WE MEN JA’TESIM BILLAHI FEKAD HUDIJE ‘ILA SIRATIN MUSTEKIMIN
  3,102,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ETTEKU ELLAHE HEKKA TUKATIHI WE LA TEMUTUNNE ‘ILLA WE ‘ENTUM MUSLIMUNE
  3,103,WE A’TESIMU BIHEBLI ELLAHI XHEMI’ÆN WE LA TEFERREKU WE EDHKURU NI’METEL-LAHI ‘ALEJKUM ‘IDH KUNTUM ‘A’DA’EN FE’ELLEFE BEJNE KULUBIKUM FE’ESBEHTUM BINI’METIHI ‘IHWANÆN WE KUNTUM ‘ALA SHEFA HUFRETIN MINE EN-NARI FE’ENKADHEKUM MINHA KEDHALIKE JUBEJJINU ELLAHU
  3,104,WE LTEKUN MINKUM ‘UMMETUN JED’UNE ‘ILAL-HAJRI WE JE’MURUNE BIL-MA’RUFI WE JENHEWNE ‘ANIL-MUNKERI WE ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-MUFLIHUNE
  3,105,WE LA TEKUNU KALLEDHINE TEFERREKU WE EHTELEFU MIN BA’DI MA XHA’EHUMUL-BEJJINATU WE ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  3,106,JEWME TEBJEDDU WUXHUHUN WE TESWEDDU WUXHUHUN FE’EMMAL-LEDHINE ESWEDDET WUXHUHUHUM ‘EKEFERTUM BA’DE ‘IMANIKUM FEDHUKUL-’ADHABE BIMA KUNTUM TEKFURUNE
  3,107,WE ‘EMMAL-LEDHINE EBJEDDET WUXHUHUHUM FEFI REHMETI ELLAHI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  3,108,TILKE ‘AJATU ELLAHI NETLUHA ‘ALEJKE BIL-HEKKI WE MALLAHU JURIDU DHULMÆN LIL’ALEMINE
  3,109,WE LILLEHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE ‘ILA ELLAHI TURXHA’UL-’UMURU
  3,110,KUNTUM HAJRE ‘UMMETIN ‘UHRIXHET LILNNASI TE’MURUNE BIL-MA’RUFI WE TENHEWNE ‘ANIL-MUNKERI WE TU’UMINUNE BILLAHI WE LEW ‘AMENE ‘EHLUL-KITABI LEKANE HAJRÆN LEHUM MINHUMUL-MU’UMINUNE WE ‘EKTHERUHUMUL-FASIKUNE
  3,111,LEN JEDURRUKUM ‘ILLA ‘EDHEN WE ‘IN JUKATILUKUM JUWELLUKUMUL-’EDBARE THUMME LA JUNSERUNE
  3,112,DURIBET ‘ALEJHIMU EDH-DHILLETU ‘EJNE MA THUKIFU ‘ILLA BIHEBLIN MINEL-LAHI WE HEBLIN MINE EN-NASI WE BA’U BIGADEBIN MINEL-LAHI WE DURIBET ‘ALEJHIMUL-MESKENETU DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KANU JEKFURUNE BI’AJATI ELLAHI WE JEKTULUNEL-’ENBIJA’E BIGAJRI HEKKIN DHALIKE
  3,113,LEJSU SEWA’EN MIN ‘EHLIL-KITABI ‘UMMETUN KA’IMETUN JETLUNE ‘AJATI ELLAHI ‘ANA’EL-LEJLI WE HUM JESXHUDUNE
  3,114,JU’UMINUNE BILLAHI WEL-JEWMIL-’AHIRI WE JE’MURUNE BIL-MA’RUFI WE JENHEWNE ‘ANIL-MUNKERI WE JUSARI’UNE FIL-HAJRATI WE ‘ULA’IKE MINE ES-SALIHINE
  3,115,WE MA JEF’ALU MIN HAJRIN FELEN JUKFERUHU WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN BIL-MUTTEKINE
  3,116,‘INNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU LEN TUGNIJE ‘ANHUM ‘EMWALUHUM WE LA ‘EWLADUHUM MINEL-LAHI SHEJ’ÆN WE ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  3,117,METHELU MA JUNFIKUNE FI HEDHIHIL-HEJÆTI ED-DUNJA KEMETHELI RIHIN FIHA SIRRUN ‘ESABET HERTHE KAWMIN DHELEMU ‘ENFUSEHUM FE’EHLEKET/HU WE MA DHELEMEHUMU ELLAHU WE LEKIN ‘ENFUSEHUM JEDHLIMUNE
  3,118,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TETTEHIDHU BITANETEN MIN DUNIKUM LA JE’LUNEKUM HABALÆN WE DDU MA ‘ANITTUM KAD BEDETIL-BEGDA’U MIN ‘EFWAHIHIM WE MA TUHFI SUDURUHUM ‘EKBERU KAD BEJJENNA LEKUMUL-’AJATI ‘IN KUNTUM TA’KILUNE
  3,119,HA’ENTUM ‘ULA’I TUHIBBUNEHUM WE LA JUHIBBUNEKUM WE TU’UMINUNE BIL-KITABI KULLIHI WE ‘IDHA LEKUKUM KALU ‘AMENNA WE ‘IDHA HALEW ‘ADDU ‘ALEJKUMUL-’ENAMILE MINEL-GAJDHI KUL MUTU BIGAJDHIKUM ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  3,120,‘IN TEMSESKUM HESENETUN TESU’UHUM WE ‘IN TUSIBKUM SEJJI’ETUN JEFREHU BIHA WE ‘IN TESBIRU WE TETTEKU LA JEDURRUKUM KEJDUHUM SHEJ’ÆN ‘INNALL-LLAHE BIMA JA’MELUNE MUHITUN
  3,121,WE ‘IDH GADEWTE MIN ‘EHLIKE TUBEWWI’UL-MU’UMININE MEKA’IDE LILKITALI WEL-LAHU SEMI’UN ‘ALIMUN
  3,122,‘IDH HEMMET TA’IFETANI MINKUM ‘EN TEFSHELA WEL-LAHU WELIJUHUMA WE ‘ALA ELLAHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MU’UMINUNE
  3,123,WE LEKAD NESEREKUMU ELLAHU BIBEDRIN WE ‘ENTUM ‘EDHILLETUN FE ETTEKU ELLAHE LE’ALLEKUM TESHKURUNE
  3,124,‘IDH TEKULU LILMU’UMININE ‘ELEN JEKFIJEKUM ‘EN JUMIDDEKUM REBBUKUM BITHELATHETI ‘ALAFIN MINEL-MELA’IKETI MUNZELINE
  3,125,BELA ‘IN TESBIRU WE TETTEKU WE JE’TUKUM MIN FEWRIHIM HADHA JUMDIDKUM REBBUKUM BIHAMSETI ‘ALAFIN MINEL-MELA’IKETI MUSEWWIMINE
  3,126,WE MA XHE’ALEHU ELLAHU ‘ILLA BUSHRA LEKUM WE LITETME’INNE KULUBUKUM BIHI WE MA EN-NESRU ‘ILLA MIN ‘INDI ELLAHIL-’AZIZIL-HEKIMI
  3,127,LIJEKTE’A TEREFÆN MINEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘EW JEKBITEHUM FEJENKALIBU HA’IBINE
  3,128,LEJSE LEKE MINEL-’EMRI SHEJ’UN ‘EW JETUBE ‘ALEJHIM ‘EW JU’ADHDHIBEHUM FE’INNEHUM DHALIMUNE
  3,129,WE LILLEHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI JEGFIRU LIMEN JESHA’U WE JU’ADHDHIBU MEN JESHA’U WEL-LAHU GAFURUN REHIMUN
  3,130,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TE’KULU ER-RIBA ‘ED’AFÆN MUDA’AFETEN WE ETTEKU ELLAHE LE’ALLEKUM TUFLIHUNE
  3,131,WE ETTEKU EN-NAREL-LETI ‘U’IDDET LILKAFIRINE
  3,132,WE ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE ER-RESULE LE’ALLEKUM TURHEMUNE
  3,133,WE SARI’U ‘ILA MEGFIRETIN MIN RABBIKUM WE XHENNETIN ‘ARDUHA ES-SEMAWATU WEL-’ERDU ‘U’IDDET LILMUTTEKINE
  3,134,EL-LEDHINE JUNFIKUNE FI ES-SERRA’I WE ED-DERRA’I WEL-KADHIMINEL-GAJDHE WEL-’AFINE ‘ANI EN-NASI WEL-LAHU JUHIBBUL-MUHSININE
  3,135,WEL-LEDHINE ‘IDHA FE’ALU FAHISHETEN ‘EW DHELEMU ‘ENFUSEHUM DHEKERU ELLAHE FASTEGFERU LIDHUNUBIHIM WE MEN JEGFIRU EDH-DHUNUBE ‘ILLALLAHU WE LEM JUSIRRU ‘ALA MA FE’ALU WE HUM JA’LEMUNE
  3,136,‘ULA’IKE XHEZA’UUHUM MEGFIRETUN MIN RABBIHIM WE XHENNATUN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA WE NI’ME ‘EXHRUL-’AMILINE
  3,137,KAD HALET MIN KABLIKUM SUNENUN FESIRU FIL-’ERDI FANDHURU KEJFE KANE ‘AKIBETUL-MUKEDHDHIBINE
  3,138,HADHA BEJANUN LILNNASI WE HUDEN WE MEW’IDHETUN LILMUTTEKINE
  3,139,WE LA TEHINU WE LA TEHZENU WE ‘ENTUMUL-’A’LEWNE ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE
  3,140,‘IN JEMSESKUM KARHUN FEKAD MESSEL-KAWME KARHUN MITHLUHU WE TILKEL-’EJJAMU NUDAWILUHA BEJNE EN-NASI WE LIJA’LEMEL-LAHUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE JETTEHIDHE MINKUM SHUHEDA’E WEL-LAHU LA JUHIBBU EDH-DHALIMINE
  3,141,WE LIJUMEHHISEL-LAHUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE JEMHEKAL-KAFIRINE
  3,142,‘EM HESIBTUM ‘EN TEDHULUL-XHENNETE WE LEMMA JA’LEMI ELLAHUL-LEDHINE XHAHEDU MINKUM WE JA’LEME ES-SABIRINE
  3,143,WE LEKAD KUNTUM TETEMENNEWNL-MEWTE MIN KABLI ‘EN TELKAWHU FEKAD RE’EJTUMUHU WE ‘ENTUM TENDHURUNE
  3,144,WE MA MUHEMMEDUN ‘ILLA RESULUN KAD HALET MIN KABLIHI ER-RUSULU ‘EFE’IN MATE ‘EW KUTILE ENKALEBTUM ‘ALA ‘A’KABIKUM WE MEN JENKALIB ‘ALA ‘AKIBEJHI FELEN JEDURREL-LAHE SHEJ’ÆN WE SEJEXHZI ELLAHU ESH-SHAKIRINE
  3,145,WE MA KANE LINEFSIN ‘EN TEMUTE ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI KITABÆN MU’UEXHXHELÆN WE MEN JURID THEWABE ED-DUNJA NU’UTIHI MINHA WE MEN JURID THEWABEL-’AHIRETI NU’UTIHI MINHA WE SENEXHZI ESH-SHAKIRINE
  3,146,WE KE’EJJIN MIN NEBIJIN KATELE ME’AHU RIBBIJUNE KETHIRUN FEMA WEHENU LIMA ‘ESABEHUM FI SEBILI ELLAHI WE MA DA’UFU WE MA ESTEKANU WEL-LAHU JUHIBBU ES-SABIRINE
  3,147,WE MA KANE KAWLEHUM ‘ILLA ‘EN KALU REBBENA EGFIR LENA DHUNUBENA WE ‘ISRAFENA FI ‘EMRINA WE THEBBIT ‘EKDAMENA WE ENSURNA ‘ALEL-KAWMIL-KAFIRINE
  3,148,FE’ATAHUMU ELLAHU THEWABE ED-DUNJA WE HUSNE THEWABIL-’AHIRETI WEL-LAHU JUHIBBUL-MUHSININE
  3,149,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IN TUTI’UL-LEDHINE KEFERU JERUDDUKUM ‘ALA ‘A’KABIKUM FETENKALIBU HASIRINE
  3,150,BELI ELLAHU MEWLAKUM WE HUWE HAJRU EN-NASIRINE
  3,151,SENULKI FI KULUBIL-LEDHINE KEFERU ER-RU’BE BIMA ‘ESHREKU BILLAHI MA LEM JUNEZZIL BIHI SULTANÆN WE ME’WAHUMU EN-NARU WE BI’SE METHWA EDH-DHALIMINE
  3,152,WE LEKAD SEDEKAKUMU ELLAHU WA’DEHU ‘IDH TEHUSSUNEHUM BI’IDHNIHI HETTA ‘IDHA FESHILTUM WE TENAZA’TUM FIL-’EMRI WE ‘ASEJTUM MIN BA’DI MA ‘ERAKUM MA TUHIBBUNE MINKUM MEN JURIDU ED-DUNJA WE MINKUM MEN JURIDUL-’AHIRETE THUMME SEREFEKUM ‘ANHUM LIJEBTELIJEKUM WE
  3,153,‘IDH TUS’IDUNE WE LA TELWUNE ‘ALA ‘EHEDIN WE ER-RESULU JED’UKUM FI ‘UHRAKUM FE’ETHABEKUM GAMMÆN BIGAMMIN LIKEJLA TEHZENU ‘ALA MA FATEKUM WE LA MA ‘ESABEKUM WEL-LAHU HABIRUN BIMA TA’MELUNE
  3,154,THUMME ‘ENZELE ‘ALEJKUM MIN BA’DIL-GAMMI ‘EMENETEN NU’ASÆN JEGSHA TA’IFETEN MINKUM WE TA’IFETUN KAD ‘EHEMMET/HUM ‘ENFUSUHUM JEDHUNNUNE BILLAHI GAJREL-HEKKI DHENNEL-XHAHILIJETI JEKULUNE HEL LENA MINEL-’EMRI MIN SHEJ’IN KUL ‘INNEL-’EMRE KULLEHU LILLAHI JUHF
  3,155,‘INNEL-LEDHINE TEWELLEW MINKUM JEWMET-TEKAL-XHEM’ANI ‘INNEMA ESTEZELLEHUMU ESH-SHEJTANU BIBA’DI MA KESEBU WE LEKAD ‘AFALLAHU ‘ANHUM ‘INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN HELIMUN
  3,156,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TEKUNU KALLEDHINE KEFERU WE KALU LI’HWANIHIM ‘IDHA DEREBU FIL-’ERDI ‘EW KANU GUZZEN LEW KANU ‘INDENA MA MATU WE MA KUTILU LIJEXH’ALEL-LAHU DHALIKE HESRETEN FI KULUBIHIM WEL-LAHU JUHJI WE JUMITU WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  3,157,WE LE’IN KUTILTUM FI SEBILI ELLAHI ‘EW MUTTUM LEMEGFIRETUN MINEL-LAHI WE REHMETUN HAJRUN MIMMA JEXHMA’UNE
  3,158,WE LE’IN MUTTUM ‘EW KUTILTUM LE’ILA ELLAHI TUHSHERUNE
  3,159,FEBIMA REHMETIN MINEL-LAHI LINTE LEHUM WE LEW KUNTE FEDHDHÆN GALIDHEL-KALBI LANFEDDU MIN HEWLIKE FA’FU ‘ANHUM WE ESTEGFIR LEHUM WE SHAWIRHUM FIL-’EMRI FE’IDHA ‘AZEMTE FETEWEKKEL ‘ALA ELLAHI ‘INNALL-LLAHE JUHIBBUL-MUTEWEKKILINE
  3,160,‘IN JENSURKUMU ELLAHU FELA GALIBE LEKUM WE ‘IN JEHDHULKUM FEMEN DHAL-LEDHI JENSURUKUM MIN BA’DIHI WE ‘ALA ELLAHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MU’UMINUNE
  3,161,WE MA KANE LINEBIJIN ‘EN JEGULLE WE MEN JEGLUL JE’TI BIMA GALLE JEWMEL-KIJAMETI THUMME TUWEFFA KULLU NEFSIN MA KESEBET WE HUM LA JUDHLEMUNE
  3,162,‘EFEMENI ETTEBE’A RIDWANEL-LAHI KEMEN BA’E BISEHATIN MINEL-LAHI WE ME’WAHU XHEHENNEMU WE BI’SEL-MESIRU
  3,163,HUM DEREXHATUN ‘INDEL-LAHI WEL-LAHU BESIRUN BIMA JA’MELUNE
  3,164,LEKAD MENNEL-LAHU ‘ALEL-MU’UMININE ‘IDH BE’ATHE FIHIM RESULÆN MIN ‘ENFUSIHIM JETLU ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATIHI WE JUZEKKIHIM WE JU’ALLIMUHUMUL-KITABE WEL-HIKMETE WE ‘IN KANU MIN KABLU LEFI DELALIN MUBININ
  3,165,‘EWELEMMA ‘ESABETKUM MUSIBETUN KAD ‘ESEBTUM MITHLEJHA KULTUM ‘ENNA HADHA KUL HUWE MIN ‘INDI ‘ENFUSIKUM ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  3,166,WE MA ‘ESABEKUM JEWMET-TEKAL-XHEM’ANI FEBI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE LIJA’LEMEL-MU’UMININE
  3,167,WE LIJA’LEMEL-LEDHINE NAFEKU WE KILE LEHUM TA’ALEW KATILU FI SEBILI ELLAHI ‘EW EDFA’U KALU LEW NA’LEMU KITALÆN LATTEBA’NAKUM HUM LILKUFRI JEWME’IDHIN ‘EKREBU MINHUM LIL’IMANI JEKULUNE BI’EFWHIHIM MA LEJSE FI KULUBIHIM WEL-LAHU ‘A’LEMU BIMA JEKTUMUNE
  3,168,EL-LEDHINE KALU LI’HWANIHIM WE KA’ADU LEW ‘ETA’UNA MA KUTILU KUL FADRE’U ‘AN ‘ENFUSIKUMUL-MEWTE ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  3,169,WE LA TEHSEBENNEL-LEDHINE KUTILU FI SEBILI ELLAHI ‘EMWATÆN BEL ‘EHJA’UN ‘INDE RABBIHIM JURZEKUNE
  3,170,FERIHINE BIMA ‘ATAHUMU ELLAHU MIN FEDLIHI WE JESTEBSHIRUNE BIEL-LEDHINE LEM JELHEKU BIHIM MIN HALFIHIM ‘ELLA HAWFUN ‘ALEJHIM WE LA HUM JEHZENUNE
  3,171,JESTEBSHIRUNE BINI’METIN MINEL-LAHI WE FEDLIN WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LA JUDI’U ‘EXHREL-MU’UMININE
  3,172,EL-LEDHINE ESTEXHABU LILLAHI WE ER-RESULI MIN BA’DI MA ‘ESABEHUMUL-KARHU LILLEDHINE ‘EHSENU MINHUM WE ETTEKAW ‘EXHRUN ‘ADHIMUN
  3,173,EL-LEDHINE KALE LEHUMU EN-NASU ‘INNE EN-NASE KAD XHEMA’U LEKUM FAHSHEWHUM FEZADEHUM ‘IMANÆN WE KALU HESBUNALLAHU WE NI’MEL-WEKILU
  3,174,FANKALEBU BINI’METIN MINEL-LAHI WE FEDLIN LEM JEMSES/HUM SU’UN WE ETTEBA’U RIDWANEL-LAHI WEL-LAHU DHU FEDLIN ‘ADHIMIN
  3,175,‘INNEMA DHELIKUMU ESH-SHEJTANU JUHAWWIFU ‘EWLIJA’EHU FELA TEHAFUHUM WE HAFUNI ‘IN KUNTUM MU’UMININE
  3,176,WE LA JEHZUNKEL-LEDHINE JUSARI’UNE FIL-KUFRI ‘INNEHUM LEN JEDURRU ELLAHE SHEJ’ÆN JURIDU ELLAHU ‘ELLA JEXH’ALE LEHUM HEDHDHÆN FIL-’AHIRETI WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ADHIMUN
  3,177,‘INNEL-LEDHINE ESHTEREWL-KUFRE BIL-’IMANI LEN JEDURRU ELLAHE SHEJ’ÆN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  3,178,WE LA JEHSEBENNEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘ENNEMA NUMLI LEHUM HAJRUN LI’ENFUSIHIM ‘INNEMA NUMLI LEHUM LIJEZDADU ‘ITHMÆN WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN MUHINUN
  3,179,MA KANEL-LAHU LIJEDHEREL-MU’UMININE ‘ALA MA ‘ENTUM ‘ALEJHI HETTA JEMIZEL-HABITHE MINET-TEJJIBI WE MA KANEL-LAHU LIJUTLI’AKUM ‘ALEL-GAJBI WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE JEXHTEBI MIN RUSULIHI MEN JESHA’U FE’AMINU BILLAHI WE RUSULIHI WE ‘IN TU’UMINU WE TETTEKU FELEKUM ‘
  3,180,WE LA JEHSEBENNEL-LEDHINE JEBHALUNE BIMA ‘ATAHUMU ELLAHU MIN FEDLIHI HUWE HAJRÆN LEHUM BEL HUWE SHERRUN LEHUM SEJUTEWWEKUNE MA BEHILU BIHI JEWMEL-KIJAMETI WE LILLEHI MIRATHU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE HABIRUN
  3,181,LEKAD SEMI’ALLAHU KAWLEL-LEDHINE KALU ‘INNALL-LLAHE FEKIRUN WE NEHNU ‘EGNIJA’U SENEKTUBU MA KALU WE KATLEHUMUL-’ENBIJA’E BIGAJRI HEKKIN WE NEKULU DHUKU ‘ADHABEL-HERIKI
  3,182,DHALIKE BIMA KADDEMET ‘EJDIKUM WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE LEJSE BIDHELLAMIN LIL’ABIDI
  3,183,EL-LEDHINE KALU ‘INNALL-LLAHE ‘AHIDE ‘ILEJNA ‘ELLA NU’UMINE LIRESULIN HETTA JE’TIJENA BIKURBANIN TE’KULUHU EN-NARU KUL KAD XHA’EKUM RUSULUN MIN KABLI BIL-BEJJINATI WE BIEL-LEDHI KULTUM FELIME KATELTUMUHUM ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  3,184,FE’IN KEDHDHEBUKE FEKAD KUDHDHIBE RUSULUN MIN KABLIKE XHA’U BIL-BEJJINATI WE EZ-ZUBURI WEL-KITABIL-MUNIRI
  3,185,KULLU NEFSIN DHA’IKATUL-MEWTI WE ‘INNEMA TUWEFFEWNE ‘UXHUREKUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI FEMEN ZUHZIHE ‘ANI EN-NARI WE ‘UDHILEL-XHENNETE FEKAD FAZE WE MAL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA ‘ILLA META’UL-GURURI
  3,186,LETUBLEWUNNE FI ‘EMWALIKUM WE ‘ENFUSIKUM WE LETESMA’UNNE MINEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-KITABE MIN KABLIKUM WE MINEL-LEDHINE ‘ESHREKU ‘EDHEN KETHIRÆN WE ‘IN TESBIRU WE TETTEKU FE’INNE DHALIKE MIN ‘AZMIL-’UMURI
  3,187,WE ‘IDH ‘EHADHEL-LAHU MITHAKAL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-KITABE LETUBEJJINUNNEHU LILNNASI WE LA TEKTUMUNEHU FENEBEDHUHU WERA’E DHUHURIHIM WE ESHTEREW BIHI THEMENÆN KALILÆN FEBI’SE MA JESHTERUNE
  3,188,LA TEHSEBENNEL-LEDHINE JEFREHUNE BIMA ‘ETEW WE JUHIBBUNE ‘EN JUHMEDU BIMA LEM JEF’ALU FELA TEHSEBENNEHUM BIMEFAZETIN MINEL-’ADHABI WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  3,189,WE LILLEHI MULKU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  3,190,‘INNE FI HALKI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE EHTILAFIL-LEJLI WE EN-NEHARI LE’AJATIN LI’WLIL-’ELBABI
  3,191,EL-LEDHINE JEDHKURUNEL-LAHE KIJAMÆN WE KU’UDÆN WE ‘ALA XHUNUBIHIM WE JETEFEKKERUNE FI HALKI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI REBBENA MA HALEKTE HADHA BATILÆN SUBHANEKE FEKINA ‘ADHABE EN-NARI
  3,192,REBBENA ‘INNEKE MEN TUDHILI EN-NARE FEKAD ‘EHZEJTEHU WE MA LILDHDHALIMINE MIN ‘ENSARIN
  3,193,REBBENA ‘INNENA SEMI’NA MUNADIÆN JUNADI LIL’IMANI ‘EN ‘AMINU BIREBBIKUM FE’AMENNA REBBENA FAGFIR LENA DHUNUBENA WE KEFFIR ‘ANNA SEJJI’ATINA WE TEWEFFENA ME’AL-’EBRARI
  3,194,REBBENA WE ‘ATINA MA WE’ADTENA ‘ALA RUSULIKE WE LA TUHZINA JEWMEL-KIJAMETI ‘INNEKE LA TUHLIFUL-MI’ADE
  3,195,FASTEXHABE LEHUM REBBUHUM ‘ENNI LA ‘UDI’U ‘AMELE ‘AMILIN MINKUM MIN DHEKERIN ‘EW ‘UNTHA BA’DUKUM MIN BA’DIN FE-EL-LEDHINE HAXHERU WE ‘UHRIXHU MIN DIJARIHIM WE ‘UDHU FI SEBILI WE KATELU WE KUTILU LE’UKEFFIRENNE ‘ANHUM SEJJI’ATIHIM WE LE’UDHILENNEHUM XHENNA
  3,196,LA JEGURRENNEKE TEKALLUBUL-LEDHINE KEFERU FIL-BILADI
  3,197,META’UN KALILUN THUMME ME’WAHUM XHEHENNEMU WE BI’SEL-MIHADU
  3,198,LEKINIL-LEDHINE ETTEKAW REBBEHUM LEHUM XHENNATUN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA NUZULÆN MIN ‘INDI ELLAHI WE MA ‘INDEL-LAHI HAJRUN LIL’EBRARI
  3,199,WE ‘INNE MIN ‘EHLIL-KITABI LEMEN JU’UMINU BILLAHI WE MA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJKUM WE MA ‘UNZILE ‘ILEJHIM HASHI’INE LILLAHI LA JESHTERUNE BI’AJATI ELLAHI THEMENÆN KALILÆN ‘ULA’IKE LEHUM ‘EXHRUHUM ‘INDE RABBIHIM ‘INNALL-LLAHE SERI’UL-HISABI
  3,200,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ESBIRU WE SABIRU WE RABITU WE ETTEKU ELLAHE LE’ALLEKUM TUFLIHUNE
  4,1,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NASU ETTEKU REBBEKUMUL-LEDHI HALEKAKUM MIN NEFSIN WAHIDETIN WE HALEKA MINHA ZEWXHEHA WE BETHTHE MINHUMA RIXHALÆN KETHIRÆN WE NISA’EN WE ETTEKU ELLAHEL-LEDHI TETESA’ELUNE BIHI WEL-’ERHAME ‘INNALL-LLAHE KANE ‘ALEJKUM REKIBÆN
  4,2,WE ‘ATUL-JETAMA ‘EMWALEHUM WE LA TETEBEDDELUL-HABITHE BIT-TEJJIBI WE LA TE’KULU ‘EMWALEHUM ‘ILA ‘EMWALIKUM ‘INNEHU KANE HUBÆN KEBIRÆN
  4,3,WE ‘IN HIFTUM ‘ELLA TUKSITU FIL-JETAMA FANKIHU MA TABE LEKUM MINE EN-NISA’ METHNA WE THULATHE WE RUBA’A FE’IN HIFTUM ‘ELLA TA’DILU FEWAHIDETEN ‘EW MA MELEKET ‘EJMANUKUM DHALIKE ‘EDNA ‘ELLA TA’ULU
  4,4,WE ‘ATU EN-NISA’ SEDUKATIHINNE NIHLETEN FE’IN TIBNE LEKUM ‘AN SHEJ’IN MINHU NEFSÆN FEKULUHU HENI’ÆN MERI’ÆN
  4,5,WE LA TU’UTU ES-SUFEHA’E ‘EMWALEKUMU ELLETI XHE’ALEL-LAHU LEKUM KIJAMÆN WE ERZUKUHUM FIHA WE EKSUHUM WE KULU LEHUM KAWLÆN MA’RUFÆN
  4,6,WE EBTELUL-JETAMA HETTA ‘IDHA BELEGU EN-NIKAHE FE’IN ‘ANESTUM MINHUM RUSHDÆN FADFA’U ‘ILEJHIM ‘EMWALEHUM WE LA TE’KULUHA ‘ISRAFÆN WE BIDARÆN ‘EN JEKBERU WE MEN KANE GANIJÆN FELJESTA’FIF WE MEN KANE FEKIRÆN FELJE’KUL BIL-MA’RUFI FE’IDHA DEFA’TUM ‘ILEJHIM ‘
  4,7,LILRRIXHALI NESIBUN MIMMA TEREKEL-WALIDANI WEL-’EKREBUNE WE LILNNISA’I NESIBUN MIMMA TEREKEL-WALIDANI WEL-’EKREBUNE MIMMA KALLE MINHU ‘EW KETHURE NESIBÆN MEFRUDÆN
  4,8,WE ‘IDHA HEDEREL-KISMETE ‘ULUL-KURBA WEL-JETAMA WEL-MESAKINU FARZUKUHUM MINHU WE KULU LEHUM KAWLÆN MA’RUFÆN
  4,9,WE LIEHSHEL-LEDHINE LEW TEREKU MIN HALFIHIM DHURRIJETEN DI’AFÆN HAFU ‘ALEJHIM FELJETTEKU ELLAHE WE LIEKULU KAWLÆN SEDIDÆN
  4,10,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JE’KULUNE ‘EMWALEL-JETAMA DHULMÆN ‘INNEMA JE’KULUNE FI BUTUNIHIM NARÆN WE SEJESLEWNE SA’IRÆN
  4,11,JUSIKUMU ELLAHU FI ‘EWLADIKUM LILDHDHEKERI MITHLU HEDHDHIL-’UNTHEJEJNI FE’IN KUNNE NISA’EN FEWKA ETHNETEJNI FELEHUNNE THULUTHA MA TEREKE WE ‘IN KANET WAHIDETEN FELEHA EN-NISFU WE LI’EBEWEJHI LIKULLI WAHIDIN MINHUMA ES-SUDUSU MIMMA TEREKE ‘IN KANE LEHU WEL
  4,12,WE LEKUM NISFU MA TEREKE ‘EZWAXHUKUM ‘IN LEM JEKUN LEHUNNE WELEDUN FE’IN KANE LEHUNNE WELEDUN FELEKUMU ER-RUBU’U MIMMA TEREKNE MIN BA’DI WESIJETIN JUSINE BIHA ‘EW DEJNIN WE LEHUNNE ER-RUBU’U MIMMA TEREKTUM ‘IN LEM JEKUN LEKUM WELEDUN FE’IN KANE LEKUM WELE
  4,13,TILKE HUDUDU ELLAHI WE MEN JUTI’I ELLAHE WE RESULEHU JUDHILHU XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA WE DHELIKEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  4,14,WE MEN JA’SI ELLAHE WE RESULEHU WE JETE’ADDE HUDUDEHU JUDHILHU NARÆN HALIDÆN FIHA WE LEHU ‘ADHABUN MUHINUN
  4,15,WEL-LATI JE’TINEL-FAHISHETE MIN NISA’IKUM FASTESH/HIDU ‘ALEJHINNE ‘ERBE’ATEN MINKUM FE’IN SHEHIDU FE’EMSIKUHUNNE FIL-BUJUTI HETTA JETEWEFFAHUNNEL-MEWTU ‘EW JEXH’ALEL-LAHU LEHUNNE SEBILÆN
  4,16,WEL-LEDHANI JE’TIJANIHA MINKUM FE’ADHUHUMA FE’IN TABA WE ‘ESLEHA FE’A’RIDU ‘ANHUMA ‘INNALL-LLAHE KANE TEWWABÆN REHIMÆN
  4,17,‘INNEMAT-TEWBETU ‘ALA ELLAHI LILLEDHINE JA’MELUNE ES-SU’E BIXHEHALETIN THUMME JETUBUNE MIN KARIBIN FE’ULA’IKE JETUBU ELLAHU ‘ALEJHIM WE KANEL-LAHU ‘ALIMÆN HEKIMÆN
  4,18,WE LEJSETIT-TEWBETU LILLEDHINE JA’MELUNE ES-SEJJI’ATI HETTA ‘IDHA HEDERE ‘EHEDEHUMUL-MEWTU KALE ‘INNI TUBTUL-’ANE WE LAL-LEDHINE JEMUTUNE WE HUM KUFFARUN ‘ULA’IKE ‘A’TEDNA LEHUM ‘ADHABÆN ‘ELIMÆN
  4,19,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA JEHILLU LEKUM ‘EN TERITHU EN-NISA’ KERHÆN WE LA TA’DULUHUNNE LITEDH/HEBU BIBA’DI MA ‘ATEJTUMUHUNNE ‘ILLA ‘EN JE’TINE BIFAHISHETIN MUBEJJINETIN WE ‘ASHIRUHUNNE BIL-MA’RUFI FE’IN KERIHTUMUHUNNE FE’ASA ‘EN TEKREHU SHEJ’ÆN WE JEX
  4,20,WE ‘IN ‘EREDTUMU ESTIBDALE ZEWXHIN MEKANE ZEWXHIN WE ‘ATEJTUM ‘IHDAHUNNE KINTARÆN FELA TE’HUDHU MINHU SHEJ’ÆN ‘ETE’HUDHUNEHU BUHTANÆN WE ‘ITHMÆN MUBINÆN
  4,21,WE KEJFE TE’HUDHUNEHU WE KAD ‘EFDA BA’DUKUM ‘ILA BA’DIN WE ‘EHADHNE MINKUM MITHAKÆN GALIDHÆN
  4,22,WE LA TENKIHU MA NEKEHE ‘ABA’UUKUM MINE EN-NISA’ ‘ILLA MA KAD SELEFE ‘INNEHU KANE FAHISHETEN WE MEKTÆN WE SA’E SEBILÆN
  4,23,HURRIMET ‘ALEJKUM ‘UMMEHATUKUM WE BENATUKUM WE ‘EHAWATUKUM WE ‘AMMATUKUM WE HALATUKUM WE BENATUL-’EHI WE BENATUL-’UHTI WE ‘UMMEHATUKUMUL-LATI ‘ERDA’NEKUM WE ‘EHAWATUKUM MINE ER-REDA’ATI WE ‘UMMEHATU NISA’IKUM WE REBA’IBUKUMUL-LATI FI HUXHURIKUM MIN NISA’I